              Access reliable, up-to-date information from verified sources and experts.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Back to Categories -->
        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <a
            href="/categories"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 font-medium text-black transition-all transform rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-yellow-500 hover:from-yellow-500 hover:to-yellow-600 hover:scale-105"
